## ğŸ¯ Objective

To help users reconnect with **self-nurturing habits often abandoned during trauma and mental health crises**, using inner child visualization and comforting micro-actions to support serotonin pathways.

**SSRIs, prescribed for serotonin-related concerns, are the leading psychiatric drug class associated with suicide-related deaths in FAERS data (2020â€“2024).** This module offers a **safe, non-pharma pathway** to support serotonin systems using inner child-focused behavioral activation.

