## ğŸ§  Rationale

- **Serotonin supports calm, structure, and emotional regulation.**
- Trauma disrupts daily rhythms, self-trust, and nurturing behaviors.
- Inner child visualization and comforting micro-actions rebuild these pathways gently.
- Consistent micro-actions stabilize serotonin pathways naturally.

